Throwable
├── Exception                               (Checked)
│   └── ApplicationException
│       ├── DataAccessException
│       │   └── DatabaseTimeoutException
│       └── BusinessException
└── RuntimeException                        (Unchecked)
    └── ApplicationRuntimeException
        ├── ValidationException
        │   └── EmailValidationException
        └── SecurityException


### All exceptions inherit from Throwable, which splits into Exception and Error.
### Under Exception, we have checked exceptions that must be handled.
### And unchecked ones that extend RuntimeException

Throwable
├── Exception                               // Represents conditions a program might handle
│   ├── Checked Exceptions                  // Must be declared or handled
│   │   ├── IOException
│   │   │   └── FileNotFoundException
│   │   └── SQLException
│   └── Unchecked Exceptions                // Extend RuntimeException
│       ├── RuntimeException
│       │   ├── NullPointerException
│       │   ├── ArithmeticException
│       │   └── IllegalArgumentException
└── Error                                   // Serious issues, not meant to be caught
    ├── OutOfMemoryError
    ├── StackOverflowError
    └── VirtualMachineError